Let no of big burgers be X,
Let no of small burgers be Y,
then,
4X + 2Y=T             (i)
X + Y=C         (ii)
from (ii),          Y=C-X
4X + 2 (C-X) =T
4X + 2C - 2X=T
2X + 2C=T
X=(T - 2C) / 2        : where T= tomatoslices and C= cheeseslices which is given.
& Y= C-X
hence {X,Y} is the answer.		   
