one of the best question of the disjoint set union concept main thing here was when to handle which query for which sorting was used we will handle the queries weight wise 

# Approach
make a disjointset class and a cmp to sort the values based on the weight sort both queries and the edgelist now coming to the logic we will go on until we get weight less than a particular query as soon we get weight greater then or equal to the query weight we fill the ans for that query now until here all the weights less than query will be under one component and hence we can fill the answer for them if they belong to same component it means they can reach there with weight less then query weight other wise they cant reach

# Complexity
